Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.30,0:54:08.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那个怪名字的小子吗\N{\rEng}You the fish with the twenty-dollar name?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.00,0:54:10.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪\N{\rEng}Hey, man, where're you going?
