Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.31,0:54:20.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.93,0:54:24.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我们就想跟你谈谈\N{\rEng}Hey! Wait! Just want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.50,0:54:26.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方  哥们\N{\rEng}Where hell are we, men?
