Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.11,0:54:33.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,快出来\N{\rEng}Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.54,0:54:34.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想伤害你\N{\rEng}We don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.12,0:54:38.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是乐手  伙计  伴奏的\N{\rEng}We're players, man. Sidemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.22,0:54:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Damn.
