Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.46,0:54:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,说得好  兄弟  说得好\N{\rEng}You can say that again, brother. You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.99,0:55:06.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那个把十种爵士混在一起演奏的人吗\N{\rEng}You the one that plays ten kinds of jazz rolled into one?
