Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.34,0:55:09.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没数过  我就是个钢琴师\N{\rEng}I've never counted them I'm just a piano player.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.80,0:55:11.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你还是开始数吧  伙计\N{\rEng}Well, you would better start counting, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.88,0:55:14.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,发明了爵士乐的人派我们来的\N{\rEng}The man who invented jazz sent us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.39,0:55:15.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.38,0:55:17.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想怎样\N{\rEng}What does he want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.49,0:55:20.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,他向你发起了钢琴决斗\N{\rEng}He challenges you to a piano duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.48,0:55:32.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰利·罗尔  你为何此次乘船去欧洲\N{\rEng}Jelly Roll, what's the reason for a trip to Europe on a steamer?
