Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.95,0:55:35.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,比密西西比河江轮更大的船\N{\rEng}anything bigger than a Mississippi riverboat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.21,0:55:37.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我对欧洲没有丝毫兴趣\N{\rEng}I don't give a damn about Europe!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.48,0:55:40.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我上这艘破船\N{\rEng}The only reason why I'm hopping this crappy tub
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.01,0:55:43.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是想拜会一位先生\N{\rEng}is because there's a gentleman I want to meet.
