Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.40,0:55:57.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,他就是在说你\N{\rEng}You bet, he's talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.48,0:56:03.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,那人说"杰利  有人的钢琴弹得比你好"\N{\rEng}...He say,"Hey, Jelly, someone plays better piano than you."
