Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.11,1:02:58.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,上  杰利·罗尔\N{\rEng}Come on, Jelly Roll,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.97,1:03:00.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我们见识一下真正的爵士乐\N{\rEng}show us what jazz is all about!
