Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.00,1:12:26.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,他只说了一句\N{\rEng}And all he said was:
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.11,1:12:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的爵士乐\N{\rEng}Fuck jazz, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.96,1:12:35.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,他就说了那一句话  "去他妈的爵士乐"\N{\rEng}That's just what he said : "Fuck jazz,too!"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.03,1:12:37.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是个不可思议的故事\N{\rEng}This is an incredible story. Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.42,1:12:39.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我错过了什么重要的事吗\N{\rEng}Did I miss anything important?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.39,1:12:40.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以这么说\N{\rEng}You couldn say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.61,1:12:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.58,1:12:42.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 \N{\rEng}Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.63,1:12:44.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友回头会跟你讲的  对吧\N{\rEng}our friend will fill you in later. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.90,1:12:46.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题  -多谢\N{\rEng}- You can count on it. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.20,1:12:48.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他很擅长编故事\N{\rEng}He's really good at telling tales.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.48,1:12:50.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是编的  先生\N{\rEng}This is no tale, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.93,1:12:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里一个人也没有\N{\rEng}There's no-one here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.49,1:12:54.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我们人太多了  吓到他了\N{\rEng}It's because there are too many of us, we've scared him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.73,1:12:56.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾  请你马上下船\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. Now, you leave this ship
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.60,1:12:58.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,不然我就逮捕你\N{\rEng}or I'll have to have you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.31,1:13:00.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,继续工作  快\N{\rEng}Get back to work. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.82,1:13:03.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会\N{\rEng}Give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.71,1:13:04.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你给我走开\N{\rEng}Piss off, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.26,1:13:07.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,明天中午这艘船就将成为过去\N{\rEng}Noon tomorrow this ship is history!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.83,1:13:18.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,放下  不然我就开枪了\N{\rEng}Stop or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.09,1:13:19.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,抓到你了\N{\rEng}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.26,1:13:22.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,老爹  冷静  是我\N{\rEng}Pops, easy, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.43,1:13:27.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,又是你吗\N{\rEng}You again? Is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.35,1:13:29.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  放下枪  好吗\N{\rEng}Yes, lower that cannon, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.01,1:13:30.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,卖掉自己的乐器\N{\rEng}Sell your instrument and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.14,1:13:33.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后再偷回去  老把戏了\N{\rEng}then steal it back, that's an old trick!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.04,1:13:35.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我早该知道你是个贼\N{\rEng}I should have known you're a thief.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.45,1:13:37.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  我在找这个\N{\rEng}No, I was looking for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.91,1:13:39.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要这个干什么\N{\rEng}And what do you need that for?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.89,1:13:41.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,人命攸关\N{\rEng}It's a matter of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.36,1:13:42.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还得借台留声机\N{\rEng}And I need a phonograph, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.86,1:13:43.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是贼还是个骗子\N{\rEng}A thief and a liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.85,1:13:46.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  老爹  我没多少时间了\N{\rEng}Look! Pops, I don't have a whole lot of time here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.10,1:13:48.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我有的是时间  鉴于我手里有把枪\N{\rEng}Well, I do! Seeing as I have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.54,1:13:50.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在想起来\N{\rEng}And now that I think of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.68,1:13:54.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候轮船上也能录唱片了\N{\rEng}since when were records made on board steamships?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.37,1:13:56.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果那首曲子真是你朋友演奏的\N{\rEng}If that music really was played by your friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.11,1:13:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么他肯定在什么时候下过船\N{\rEng}it means that at some time in his life he got off that ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.75,1:14:00.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\rEng}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.70,1:14:02.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可能  老爹\N{\rEng}Not a chance, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.32,1:14:05.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这张充满激情的唱片是他亲自演奏的\N{\rEng}He cut this passionate recording personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.32,1:14:07.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是他最好的作品\N{\rEng}I think it's his best work!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.16,1:14:11.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他并没下过船  一秒都没有\N{\rEng}But he didn't jump ship to do it, not even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.78,1:14:14.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,您的前途无可限量  1900先生\N{\rEng}The sky's the limit Mr. Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.52,1:14:18.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这张唱片热卖的话  这我们有信心\N{\rEng}If this record sells like hotcakes and we think it will,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.55,1:14:20.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,您将会扬名立万  19先生\N{\rEng}you'll go far, Mr. Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.08,1:14:23.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,介意我喊你19吗\N{\rEng}Do you mind if I call you Nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.21,1:14:25.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会疼吧\N{\rEng}This is going to hurt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.38,1:14:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了  先生们  数到三\N{\rEng}Ready now, gentelmen. On the count.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.55,1:14:31.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,一  二  三\N{\rEng}And one, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.20,1:17:29.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  19\N{\rEng}Oh, Nineteen!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.20,1:17:35.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是天籁之音  这曲子叫什么\N{\rEng}That is one amazing piece of music. What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.49,1:17:39.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们会感动得泪流满面\N{\rEng}It's going to have people crying buckets.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.87,1:17:41.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,得起一个合适的名字\N{\rEng}It's got to have the right title though,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.79,1:17:43.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,朗朗上口的\N{\rEng}something catchy like....
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.42,1:17:45.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,像是《随风摇曳》之类的\N{\rEng}"Swinging in the Breeze" or...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.14,1:17:48.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,很美  一如既往\N{\rEng}Great, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.18,1:17:50.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,《美妙的19》  就这个了\N{\rEng}..."Sweet Nineteen," That's it...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.04,1:17:52.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会大获成功的\N{\rEng}You're going to be big time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.36,1:17:55.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要迈出那一大步\N{\rEng}And all you got to do is take that big step.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.88,1:18:00.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么一大步\N{\rEng}What big step?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.38,1:18:02.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,下船\N{\rEng}Getting off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.84,1:18:06.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,走下这破甲板  去追逐...\N{\rEng}Getting off these lousy planks of wood and going after...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.69,1:18:11.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,追逐属于你的名和利\N{\rEng}going after your fame and fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.22,1:18:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想多嘴  伙计们  但是\N{\rEng}I don't mean to butt in, fellas, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.01,1:18:18.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,有了这个  你不必下船\N{\rEng}with this, you can have anything
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.37,1:18:22.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,就能得到你想要的一切\N{\rEng}you want and never have to set foot off this boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.01,1:18:41.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会发行数百万张唱片\N{\rEng}We'll print millions of copies,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.72,1:18:43.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样全世界的人\N{\rEng}so that people all over the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.56,1:18:47.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,都能欣赏你美妙的演奏了  19\N{\rEng}world can hear your wonderful music, Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.34,1:18:49.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,19先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.57,1:18:52.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让我的音乐离开我\N{\rEng}I won't let my music go anywhere without me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.17,1:18:56.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  别碰\N{\rEng}No! Don't touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.16,1:18:57.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么  你不能这样\N{\rEng}What are you doing? You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.25,1:19:00.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们签了合同  你不能反悔\N{\rEng}We have a contract. You can't go back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.97,1:19:02.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我总是反悔\N{\rEng}I always go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.51,1:20:03.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\rEng}Miss,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.89,1:20:11.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我将不胜荣幸...\N{\rEng}I'd be pleased if you...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.89,1:20:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\rEng}Miss,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.50,1:20:27.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我将...\N{\rEng}I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.03,1:20:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我将万分激动\N{\rEng}I'd be thrilled...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.04,1:20:35.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你肯接受这...\N{\rEng}if you'd accept this...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.46,1:20:41.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,微薄之礼\N{\rEng}small token...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.35,1:21:54.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,帕多安小姐  你一个人在这儿做什么\N{\rEng}Hey, Miss Padoan, what are you doing here all alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.14,1:21:56.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,数浪花吗\N{\rEng}Counting the waves?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.14,1:21:59.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,船长说我们就要跨过北回归线了\N{\rEng}The captain said we'd be passing the Tropic of Cancer soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.17,1:22:01.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  好歹有点景色可看了\N{\rEng}Great! At least we'll have something to look at.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.94,1:22:05.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到大海在变颜色吗  一天十次\N{\rEng}You ever notice how the sea changes colors? Ten times a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.39,1:22:06.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不止呢\N{\rEng}Even more.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.74,1:22:09.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看一整天的海\N{\rEng}I could look at the sea all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.53,1:22:11.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,农民是不看海的\N{\rEng}You know farmers don't ever look at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.35,1:22:13.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们怕海  至少我听说是这样\N{\rEng}It scares them, at least that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.19,1:22:15.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的\N{\rEng}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.67,1:22:20.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一次  我父亲告诉我他听到了大海的声音\N{\rEng}Once, my father told me he heard the ocean's voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.25,1:22:23.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  大海说了什么\N{\rEng}Really? What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.43,1:22:26.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你  这是秘密\N{\rEng}I can't tell you. It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.11,1:22:28.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,秘密是不能说出去的\N{\rEng}And secrets should be kept.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.72,1:22:30.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,天  雨真下大了\N{\rEng}Gosh, it's really coming down now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.98,1:22:32.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们进去吧\N{\rEng}Let's get back inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.78,1:22:34.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我挽着你\N{\rEng}Let me take your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.60,1:23:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}女士三等舱
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.25,1:27:01.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,请让一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.50,1:27:05.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,请让一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.81,1:27:07.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,请让一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.42,1:27:10.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,小姐  请等等\N{\rEng}Please, miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.89,1:27:14.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有话跟你说\N{\rEng}I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.95,1:27:18.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是去见你父亲  对吗\N{\rEng}You're meeting your father, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.95,1:27:20.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.73,1:27:22.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\rEng}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.46,1:27:24.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我见过他\N{\rEng}I think I've met him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.83,1:27:29.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这艘船上\N{\rEng}On this ship,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.81,1:27:31.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,好几年前\N{\rEng}quite a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.51,1:27:35.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是不是跟我坐的同一艘船\N{\rEng}I don't know if he took this same ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.49,1:27:39.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定\N{\rEng}I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.26,1:27:43.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他有一支小风笛  对吗\N{\rEng}He has a musette. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.96,1:27:47.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起演奏过\N{\rEng}I think we played together.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.14,1:27:50.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是否还记得  但...\N{\rEng}I don't know if he'd remember, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.45,1:27:53.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,请帮我带个好\N{\rEng}say hello to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.00,1:27:54.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  我会的\N{\rEng}All right, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.46,1:27:57.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你是怎么知道我是谁的\N{\rEng}But how did you know who I was?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.12,1:27:59.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊  不是吗\N{\rEng}It's very strange, no?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.19,1:28:01.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是秘密\N{\rEng}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.45,1:28:05.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,秘密是不能说出去的\N{\rEng}And secrets should be kept.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.50,1:28:08.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过你父亲当年却对我吐露了秘密\N{\rEng}Although I think your father felt differently back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.03,1:28:12.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,快往前走\N{\rEng}Come on! Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.08,1:28:14.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,照这速度我们得在这儿待一周了\N{\rEng}Or we'll be here all week at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.99,1:28:37.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,请你收下这...微薄的音乐礼物\N{\rEng}Please accept this... small musical token.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.74,1:28:40.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我听不到你在说什么\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, but I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.87,1:28:43.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你...\N{\rEng}I want you to...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.67,1:28:47.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,收下这份微薄之礼\N{\rEng} accept this small token.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.88,1:28:50.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听不到你在说什么\N{\rEng}I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.06,1:28:56.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\rEng}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.49,1:28:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  也祝你好运\N{\rEng}Thank you. Good luck to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.52,1:29:03.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你哪天来看看我们吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you come and visit us some day?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.11,1:29:06.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们住在莫特街27号\N{\rEng}We live on Mott Street. Number 27.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.23,1:29:08.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲开了家鱼店\N{\rEng}My father has a fish shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.72,1:29:11.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rEng}Maybe....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.50,1:29:20.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,帕多安  好了  下一个\N{\rEng}Padoan, okay. Next.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.90,1:29:21.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\rEng}Next.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.06,1:30:02.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,他再也没跟我提起那个姑娘  我也没问起\N{\rEng}He never mentioned her to me again, and I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.74,1:30:05.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少在随后的12次往返航程中没有\N{\rEng}At least not for the next twelve crossings.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:08.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外  他就如之前一样快活\N{\rEng}Besides, he was happy just like always.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.17,1:30:11.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,他受欢迎的程度也到达了顶峰\N{\rEng}His popularity was at its peak.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.16,1:30:13.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后春天的一个晚上\N{\rEng}Then, one evening in spring,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.58,1:30:16.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,在热那亚到纽约的途中\N{\rEng}halfway between Genoa and New York,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.56,1:30:18.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在大海上\N{\rEng}right in the middle of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.45,1:30:21.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,三天后  我们到纽约时  \N{\rEng}In three days when we get to New York,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.02,1:30:25.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要下船\N{\rEng}I'm getting off this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.88,1:30:29.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不说话\N{\rEng}Cat got your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.16,1:30:35.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我很高兴\N{\rEng}No, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.04,1:30:38.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,但怎么这么突然\N{\rEng}But all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.40,1:30:43.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计\N{\rEng}My man...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.53,1:30:45.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这太棒了\N{\rEng}That's aces.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.81,1:30:47.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去陆地上看点东西\N{\rEng}I've got to see something down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.67,1:30:48.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.17,1:30:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,大海\N{\rEng}The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.74,1:30:56.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你开玩笑吧\N{\rEng}You're pulling my leg?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.81,1:31:00.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,从你出生那天起  你就只见过大海\N{\rEng}You've seen nothing but the ocean since the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.77,1:31:01.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是在船上\N{\rEng}But from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.10,1:31:05.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去陆地上看  这完全是两码事\N{\rEng}I want to see it from there. It's not the same thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.27,1:31:09.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,等我们靠岸  在船边俯身好好看看不就得了\N{\rEng}Wait till we dock, lean over the side, take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.98,1:31:11.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是一码事\N{\rEng}It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.12,1:31:13.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\rEng}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.84,1:31:16.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,在陆上  你能听到大海的声音\N{\rEng}From land, you can hear its voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.89,1:31:18.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,在船上可听不到\N{\rEng}You don't hear that from a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.98,1:31:21.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫大海的声音\N{\rEng}What do you mean, its voice?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.18,1:31:23.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,大海的声音\N{\rEng}Its voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.81,1:31:28.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像是...\N{\rEng}It's like...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.30,1:31:32.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,喊叫声\N{\rEng}a big scream...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.35,1:31:38.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你生活是无限的\N{\rEng}telling you that life is immense.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.66,1:31:40.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,等你听到了\N{\rEng}Once you've finally heard it,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.72,1:31:43.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,就会知道要如何才能继续生活下去\N{\rEng}then you really know what you have to do to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.20,1:31:46.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在这儿待一辈子\N{\rEng}I could stay here forever,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.18,1:31:52.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,但大海什么都不会告诉我\N{\rEng}but the ocean would never tell me a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.39,1:31:57.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我下船  在陆上住两年\N{\rEng}But if I get off, live on land for a couple of years,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.99,1:32:01.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就会变成凡人  跟别人一样\N{\rEng}then I'll be normal. Just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.24,1:32:06.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许有一天  我会去海边\N{\rEng}Then maybe one day, I'll make it to the coast,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.00,1:32:10.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞭望大海  听到它的喊叫\N{\rEng}look up, see the ocean, and hear it scream.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.85,1:32:15.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这些屁话都是谁告诉你的\N{\rEng}I don't know who's been telling you all this bullshit
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.07,1:32:16.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是你自己编的\N{\rEng}or if you're just making it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.19,1:32:18.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你知道我怎么想的吗\N{\rEng}But you want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.93,1:32:19.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\rEng}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.11,1:32:25.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想下船  其实是为了那个姑娘\N{\rEng}the real reason you want off this ship is the girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.17,1:32:27.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,总是这样\N{\rEng}It's always the girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.18,1:32:31.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,但即使不是为了这个  我也不介意\N{\rEng}But even if it's not the reason, that suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.60,1:32:34.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我一直希望你能下船\N{\rEng}Because I've always wanted you to leave this ship
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.89,1:32:36.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,给陆上的人演奏\N{\rEng}and play for the people on land.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.82,1:32:40.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,娶个好女人  生几个孩子\N{\rEng}And marry a nice woman and have children,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.43,1:32:44.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,得到生活中其他没有无限那么夸张\N{\rEng}and all those things in life which are not immense
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.79,1:32:48.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,但却是值得拥有的东西\N{\rEng}but are worth the effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.37,1:32:52.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会来看我吧  麦克斯\N{\rEng}You'll come visit me, won't you, Max?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.30,1:32:54.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,来陆上看我\N{\rEng}On land?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.24,1:32:56.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\rEng}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.61,1:33:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样你就能给我介绍你孩子的母亲\N{\rEng}That way, you'll introduce me to the mother of your children,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.49,1:33:05.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,邀请我周日来进晚餐\N{\rEng}and invite me for Sunday dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.69,1:33:09.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会带甜点和一瓶酒来\N{\rEng}I'll bring the dessert and a bottle of wine
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.76,1:33:11.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你对我说"你太客气了"\N{\rEng}and you'll tell me I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.19,1:33:16.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你带我参观你的家\N{\rEng}And while you're showing me around your house
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.13,1:33:18.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你家盖得像艘船\N{\rEng}shaped like a ship,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.78,1:33:21.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子则在烤火鸡\N{\rEng}your wife will be cooking a turkey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.17,1:33:22.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起围坐在餐桌旁\N{\rEng}And then we'll sit at the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.82,1:33:25.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会赞美她的厨艺\N{\rEng}I'll tell her she's an excellent cook,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.64,1:33:29.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,她则说你总谈起我\N{\rEng}and she'll say how you talk about me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.33,1:33:36.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要把我的驼绒大衣给你\N{\rEng}You know, I'm going to give you my camel coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.36,1:33:40.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你穿去陆上会很帅气\N{\rEng}You'll cut a fine figure when you get down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.51,1:33:47.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我曾见过多少人在码头道别\N{\rEng}How many people I have seen saying goodbye on the docks
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.91,1:33:49.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实心里毫不在乎\N{\rEng}without giving a damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.64,1:33:55.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我跟1900道别的时候  心里真不是滋味\N{\rEng}But when I said goodbye to Nineteen Hundred, it was a real blow.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.74,1:33:58.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们笑着  不停说"回头见"\N{\rEng}We laughed, we kept saying "See you soon",
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.10,1:34:03.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,但心里却知道我们再也不会见面了\N{\rEng}But inside, we both knew we'd never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.93,1:34:23.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-再见  -再见  1900  保重啊\N{\rEng}- Bye, bye. - Goodbye, Nineteen Hundred, take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.15,1:34:24.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-再见  -好好玩\N{\rEng}- Goodbye! - Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.75,1:34:28.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,冬天记得穿羊毛背心\N{\rEng}Remember to wear your woollen vest in winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.29,1:34:30.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,保重啊  1900  保重\N{\rEng}Take care Nineteen Hundred, take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.56,1:34:32.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时间给我们写信\N{\rEng}Write us a letter sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.16,1:34:35.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,-保重  -代我们向百老汇问好\N{\rEng}- Take care yourself! - Give my regards to Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.05,1:35:10.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了  踩着屎了吗\N{\rEng}What'd he do, step in shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.37,1:35:13.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能是忘了什么\N{\rEng}Maybe he just forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.14,1:35:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能是忘了他为什么要下船了\N{\rEng}Maybe he's forgotten why he's getting off.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.79,1:37:13.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,之后很久他一直怪怪的\N{\rEng}He was strange for a long time after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.12,1:37:16.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不跟人说话\N{\rEng}He wouldn't talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.27,1:37:20.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,接连几天就自己待着\N{\rEng}He preferred keeping to himself for days and days.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.64,1:37:24.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,他似乎在思考很隐私的事\N{\rEng}He seemed taken by very personal matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.80,1:37:28.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,-然后  有一天  -瞧啊\N{\rEng}- Then, one day, - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.31,1:37:30.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正坐在酒吧里\N{\rEng}while I was sitting at the bar...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.81,1:37:41.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你的大衣  麦克斯  很合身\N{\rEng}Thanks for the coat, Max. Fit like a glove.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.80,1:37:44.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊\N{\rEng}It was a real shame.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.73,1:37:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我好多了\N{\rEng}I'm much better now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.87,1:37:50.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,不再想那些了\N{\rEng}I'm done with all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.82,1:38:10.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像以前一样\N{\rEng}Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.62,1:38:29.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,1993年8月21日  我离开了弗吉尼亚号\N{\rEng}I left the Virginian on August 21st, 1933,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.90,1:38:34.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,证件  欠付工资  一样不差\N{\rEng}with my leave papers and back pay. Everything in order.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.42,1:38:37.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我迟早会离开大海\N{\rEng}I knew that sooner or later I'd have been through with the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.69,1:38:39.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我离开了\N{\rEng}So that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.58,1:38:44.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我再也没听说1900和弗吉尼亚号\N{\rEng}I heard no more about Nineteen Hundred or the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.69,1:38:46.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我从未忘记过\N{\rEng}Not that I ever forgot them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.07,1:38:48.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反\N{\rEng}On the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.25,1:38:51.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,战时我常自问\N{\rEng}During the war, I'd always ask myself...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.30,1:38:55.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果1900在这儿  他会怎么做\N{\rEng}Who knows what Nineteen Hundred would do if he were here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.02,1:38:57.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会说什么\N{\rEng}Who knows what he'd say?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.52,1:39:00.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会说  去他妈的战争\N{\rEng}Fuck war, he'd say.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.13,1:39:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,但从我嘴里说出来  感觉就不一样了\N{\rEng}But said by me, it wasn't the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.78,1:39:22.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,都那么多年了\N{\rEng}A lot of time's gone by, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.34,1:39:24.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他没走呢\N{\rEng}Who could say he really didn't leave?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.90,1:39:26.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许有一天  他真的去了莫特街\N{\rEng}Maybe one fine day, he actually went to Mott Street,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.63,1:39:28.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,去了那家鱼店  去找那个女人\N{\rEng}the fish shop, and asked for the woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.59,1:39:30.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\rEng}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.18,1:43:01.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,康恩号  你怎么了  晕船了吗\N{\rEng}Hey, Conn, what's the matter? You lose your sea legs?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.94,1:43:07.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪找到那唱片的\N{\rEng}Where the hell did you find that record?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.92,1:43:14.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这些年都在干什么\N{\rEng}What have you been up to all these years?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.22,1:43:22.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,演奏\N{\rEng}Making music.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.66,1:43:25.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,战时也是吗\N{\rEng}Even during the war?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.74,1:43:32.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,即使没人跳舞了\N{\rEng}Even when no one was dancing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.20,1:43:38.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,即使遭到轰炸\N{\rEng}Even when the bombs were falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.82,1:43:42.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直演奏\N{\rEng}And I kept playing
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.18,1:43:45.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到船到了这儿\N{\rEng}till the ship got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.59,1:43:52.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这还叫船吗\N{\rEng}Call this a ship?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.85,1:43:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,快要爆炸的炸药山差不多\N{\rEng}It's more like a mountain of dynamite about to explode.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.06,1:44:01.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,有点危险啊  是不是\N{\rEng}A bit dangerous, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.68,1:44:08.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你呢  麦克斯\N{\rEng}And you, Max?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.56,1:44:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的小号呢\N{\rEng}Where's your trumpet?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.26,1:44:16.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我放弃了  有一段日子了\N{\rEng}I gave it up as well, a while back.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.67,1:44:22.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我挺想重新开始\N{\rEng}But, you know, now I'm in the mood for starting again.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.95,1:44:25.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我满脑子都是点子\N{\rEng}I'm busting with new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.80,1:44:29.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们演二重奏吧  你和我\N{\rEng}Let's start a duo, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.01,1:44:32.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者组建自己的乐队\N{\rEng}Or our own band:
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.82,1:44:40.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼·布德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900大乐队\N{\rEng}The "Danny Boodman T.D. Lemon nineteen Hundred Big Band!"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.41,1:44:42.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,想想都激动\N{\rEng}It gets the blood going!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.40,1:44:44.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会声名大噪的\N{\rEng}We'd be a smash.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.47,1:44:51.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  1900  跟我下船\N{\rEng}Come on, Nineteen Hundred. Come with me. Let's get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.50,1:44:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在码头上看船炸飞\N{\rEng}We'll watch the fireworks from the pier,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.65,1:44:55.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后从零开始\N{\rEng}and then we'll start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.89,1:45:00.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时候就得这样\N{\rEng}Sometimes that's the way you have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.91,1:45:03.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,从头开始\N{\rEng}You go right back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.40,1:45:17.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要你还有一个好故事  \N{\rEng}"You're never really done for
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.81,1:45:21.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,还可以找个人讲讲\N{\rEng}as long as you've got a good story
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.24,1:45:23.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,就还不算完\N{\rEng}and someone to tell it to".
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.52,1:45:25.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗\N{\rEng}Remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.03,1:45:29.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你说的\N{\rEng}You told me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.76,1:45:36.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在有多少故事啊\N{\rEng}Well, what a stack of stories you got now!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.90,1:45:40.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,世界会聆听你的每一句话\N{\rEng}The world would be hanging on your every word,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.93,1:45:45.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会为你的音乐发狂\N{\rEng}and they'd go crazy for your music.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.08,1:45:49.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\rEng}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.77,1:45:53.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,那大城市\N{\rEng}All that city. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.38,1:46:01.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,看不到尽头\N{\rEng}You just couldn't see an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.36,1:46:05.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,尽头\N{\rEng}The end!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.27,1:46:08.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rEng}Please?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.80,1:46:12.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我尽头在哪吗\N{\rEng}You please just show me where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.88,1:46:18.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,走在舷梯上感觉很好\N{\rEng}It was all very fine on that gangway
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.21,1:46:23.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我穿着那件大衣  真是气派\N{\rEng}and I was grand, too, in my overcoat.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.05,1:46:25.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,挺帅气的\N{\rEng}I cut quite a figure.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.16,1:46:31.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我当时是真的想下船\N{\rEng}And I was getting off, guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.43,1:46:35.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,问题不在那儿\N{\rEng}That's wasn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.03,1:46:43.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我停下的不是我看到的东西  麦克斯\N{\rEng}It wasn't what I saw that stopped me, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.98,1:46:46.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我没看到的\N{\rEng}It was what I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.35,1:46:49.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\rEng}Can you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.66,1:46:53.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看不到的\N{\rEng}What I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.82,1:46:59.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,城市一望无际  我就是看不到尽头\N{\rEng}In all that sprawling city, there was everything except an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.11,1:47:02.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有尽头\N{\rEng}There was no end.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.39,1:47:07.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就是看不到  \N{\rEng}What I did not see
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.30,1:47:10.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪里是尽头\N{\rEng}was where the whole thing came to an end,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.16,1:47:14.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,世界的尽头\N{\rEng}the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.91,1:47:24.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,比方说  钢琴\N{\rEng}You take a piano.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.96,1:47:30.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,琴键有始有终\N{\rEng}Keys begin, the keys end.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.21,1:47:35.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道有88个琴键  谁都不能否认\N{\rEng}You know there are 88 of them, nobody can tell you any different.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.73,1:47:40.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,琴键是有限的  你是无限的\N{\rEng}They are not infinite, you are infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.87,1:47:47.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能在琴键上演奏出的音乐是无限的\N{\rEng}And on those keys, the music that you can make is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.69,1:47:50.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样\N{\rEng}I like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.30,1:47:52.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,这我能接受\N{\rEng}That I can live by.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.01,1:47:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,可我走上舷梯\N{\rEng}You get me up on that gangway
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.15,1:47:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我面前铺开的\N{\rEng}and you roll out in front of me
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.51,1:47:58.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,是成百上千\N{\rEng}a keyboard of millions of keys,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.41,1:48:00.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万的琴键  永无止境\N{\rEng}millions and billions of keys that never end.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.56,1:48:04.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是如此  麦克斯  永无止境\N{\rEng}And that's the truth, Max, that they never end.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.69,1:48:06.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,那琴键是无限的\N{\rEng}That keyboard is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.31,1:48:09.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果琴键是无限的\N{\rEng}And if that keyboard is infinite,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.53,1:48:12.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么你在那琴键上是无法演奏的\N{\rEng}then on that keyboard there is no music you can play.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.24,1:48:15.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你坐错了长凳\N{\rEng}You're sitting on the wrong bench.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.55,1:48:19.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是上帝的钢琴\N{\rEng}That's God's piano.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.22,1:48:25.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊  你看到那些街道了吗\N{\rEng}Christ, did you see the streets?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.19,1:48:28.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,就那些街道都有几千条啊\N{\rEng}Just the streets. There were thousands of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.81,1:48:32.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么办啊  怎么选择一条街道\N{\rEng}How do you do it down there? How do you choose just one?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.80,1:48:35.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个女人\N{\rEng}One woman,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.77,1:48:37.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,一栋房子\N{\rEng}one house,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.43,1:48:41.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,一块属于你的地方\N{\rEng}one piece of land to call your own,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.47,1:48:43.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,一片你可以欣赏的风景\N{\rEng}one landscape to look at,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.33,1:48:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,一种死去的方式\N{\rEng}one way to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.18,1:48:52.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么大的世界压在你身上\N{\rEng}All that world just weighing down on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.84,1:48:54.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不知道哪里是尽头\N{\rEng}You don't even know where it comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.91,1:48:56.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不怕自己\N{\rEng}I mean, aren't you ever just scared of
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.79,1:48:59.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,想到这些会崩溃吗\N{\rEng}breaking apart at the thought of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.04,1:49:01.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,不怕如此生活是多大的负担\N{\rEng}At the enormity of living it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.96,1:49:06.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我生在这艘船上\N{\rEng}I was born on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.99,1:49:11.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这世界从我身边走过\N{\rEng}And the world passed me by,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.48,1:49:17.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,每次只有两千人\N{\rEng}but two thousand people at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.30,1:49:21.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有梦想\N{\rEng}And there were wishes here,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.37,1:49:27.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那些梦想不会超出船的范围\N{\rEng}but never more than fit between prow and stern.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.46,1:49:33.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在一架有限的钢琴上  可以演奏你的幸福\N{\rEng}You played out your happiness on a piano that was not infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.26,1:49:35.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我生活的方式\N{\rEng}I learned to live that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.80,1:49:40.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,陆地\N{\rEng}Land?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.06,1:49:46.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,陆地对我来说  是一艘太大的船\N{\rEng}Land is a ship too big for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.91,1:49:52.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,是太美的女人\N{\rEng}It's a woman too beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.71,1:49:56.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,是太长的航程\N{\rEng}It's a voyage too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.21,1:49:59.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,是太浓烈的香水\N{\rEng}Perfume too strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.61,1:50:03.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我不会演奏的音乐\N{\rEng}It's music I don't know how to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.10,1:50:07.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能下船\N{\rEng}I could never get off this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.70,1:50:15.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我至多可以死去\N{\rEng}At best, I can step off my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.69,1:50:22.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟  对世人来说  我并不存在\N{\rEng}After all, I don't exist for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.60,1:50:28.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是例外  麦克斯\N{\rEng}You're the exception, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.29,1:50:33.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有你知道我在这儿\N{\rEng}You're the only one who knows that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.41,1:50:37.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是唯一的\N{\rEng}You're a minority.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.04,1:50:40.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得接受这个现实\N{\rEng}And you'd better get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.93,1:50:47.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我的朋友\N{\rEng}Forgive me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.01,1:50:51.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会下船\N{\rEng}But I'm not getting off.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.90,1:52:20.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,麦克斯\N{\rEng}Hey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.96,1:52:25.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,想象我站在天堂门口\N{\rEng}Picture the scene at the Golden Gates.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.08,1:52:29.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个人在一张名单上找我的名字  却找不到\N{\rEng}Some guy searching a list trying to find my name, not finding it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.98,1:52:32.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说你叫什么来着\N{\rEng}What did you say your name was again?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.13,1:52:34.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,1900\N{\rEng}Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.00,1:52:39.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,尼曼  南丁格尔  奈斯托克  \N{\rEng}Niemann, Nightingale, Ninestock...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.73,1:52:41.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,尼德丁\N{\rEng}Nittledeen?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.04,1:52:43.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  是这样  我出生在船上\N{\rEng}Well, you see, sir. I was born on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.53,1:52:45.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\rEng}Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.75,1:52:48.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都在一艘船上\N{\rEng}Born, raised, and died on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.56,1:52:50.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,那上面可能没有我的名字\N{\rEng}Maybe I'm not registered there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.49,1:52:53.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛  船失事了\N{\rEng}Yeah, shipwreck?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.77,1:52:56.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是  是被六吨半的炸药炸飞\N{\rEng}No, six and a half tons of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.61,1:53:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在好点了吧\N{\rEng}Feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.25,1:53:05.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的  就是缺了只胳膊\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm fine, except I lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.96,1:53:07.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊\N{\rEng}An arm?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.83,1:53:09.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸时炸飞的\N{\rEng}Yes, in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.28,1:53:14.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去那边应该能找到一只\N{\rEng}Well, you should be able to find one over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.81,1:53:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你缺了哪只胳膊来着\N{\rEng}Which one did you say you were missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.23,1:53:19.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,左胳膊  先生\N{\rEng}Left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.01,1:53:23.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是太抱歉了\N{\rEng}I'm dreadfully sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.22,1:53:27.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们这儿好像只有两只右胳膊\N{\rEng}We only seem to have two rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.75,1:53:30.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,两只右胳膊\N{\rEng}Two right arms?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.13,1:53:31.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.82,1:53:33.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样\N{\rEng}Afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.11,1:53:37.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你介不介意...\N{\rEng}Would you mind awfully if....
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.24,1:53:40.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}If I what?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.57,1:53:44.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿一只右胳膊顶一下\N{\rEng}Well, if you take a right arm instead of a left?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.83,1:53:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,说起来\N{\rEng}Well, all things considered,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.71,1:53:53.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,有只右胳膊总比没有好吧\N{\rEng}better a right arm than nothing, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.03,1:53:56.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,说得太对了\N{\rEng}Couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.65,1:54:00.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可不好笑啊  麦克斯\N{\rEng}No laughing matter, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.74,1:54:04.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是够呛\N{\rEng}What a cock-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.63,1:54:08.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,永远长着两只右胳膊\N{\rEng}Spend eternity with two right arms?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.47,1:54:11.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么划十字啊\N{\rEng}I mean, how would you make the sign of the cross?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.01,1:54:28.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,麦克斯\N{\rEng}Hey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.71,1:54:33.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,想象我用两只右手能演奏怎样的音乐\N{\rEng}Imagine the music I could play with two right arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.98,1:54:36.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望那上面有钢琴\N{\rEng}Hope I can find a piano up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.41,1:54:47.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,一起使劲\N{\rEng}One, oh, together now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.87,1:56:21.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是我  你会怎么做\N{\rEng}What would you have done in my shoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.55,1:56:24.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.03,1:56:32.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我大概会觉得自己很没用\N{\rEng}I would probably have felt quite useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.72,1:56:41.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有的故事都终会结束  \N{\rEng}Sooner or later all stories end,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.71,1:56:44.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,再没什么可讲的了\N{\rEng}and there's nothing left to add.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.93,1:56:52.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  谢了  老爹\N{\rEng}Anyhow, thanks, pops.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.37,1:57:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,康恩号\N{\rEng}Conn,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.85,1:57:17.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有一件事我不懂\N{\rEng}there's just one thing I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.35,1:57:22.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是谁把碎唱片藏在钢琴里的\N{\rEng}Who hid the broken record inside the piano?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.12,1:57:23.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rEng}You're looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.58,1:57:28.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你也不是那么没用了\N{\rEng}So you weren't so useless after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.45,1:57:37.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,康恩号\N{\rEng}Conn.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.00,1:57:42.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.25,1:57:48.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的小号\N{\rEng}Take your trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.81,1:57:51.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会用得上的\N{\rEng}Well, you'll be needing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.52,1:57:56.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用给钱了\N{\rEng}Never mind the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.79,1:58:01.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个好故事比一把旧小号珍贵多了\N{\rEng}A good story's worth more than an old trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.64,1:58:10.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢了  老爹\N{\rEng}Okay, Pops.

